  "A carpenter cuts a board into two pieces. One piece is 3 feet longer than the other. If the total length is 15 feet, she writes: x + (x + 3) = 15. But her helper says the equation for one piece is just x + 3 = 15. Whose equation gives the length of the shorter piece?": "",
